It's lamb.

603
00:31:47,055 --> 00:31:49,662
I'm thinking I might have a boot for you, too.

604
00:31:50,051 --> 00:31:51,744
Any ideas where I can put it?

605
00:31:51,884 --> 00:31:55,271
