618
00:32:48,410 --> 00:32:49,525
He's housesitting...

619
00:32:49,913 --> 00:32:51,172
for Nicolas cage.

620
00:32:51,248 --> 00:32:53,981
That's lisa marie in the framed photo on the bar.

621
00:32:54,958 --> 00:33:00,488
And, finally, it appears as though he did do some research into your background,

622
