Here.

635
00:33:46,829 --> 00:33:47,656
Can you file this under

636
00:33:47,732 --> 00:33:52,143
"cases I don't have time for that my disobedient daughter can take behind my back"?

637
00:33:53,531 --> 00:33:54,570
I'm really sorry.

638
00:33:54,729 --> 00:33:55,332
For what?

639
00:33:56,387 --> 00:33:58,240
Taking the case or getting caught?

640
00:33:59,104 --> 00:34:00,410
Okay, for both.

641
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,610
I just thought it was crazy to pass up that amount of money,

642
00:34:03,686 --> 00:34:04,838
and I thought I could handle it.

643
00:34:04,914 --> 00:34:07,329
You always think you can handle it, Veronica.

644
00:34:07,438 --> 00:34:11,395
Believe it or not, at 18, you can't handle everything.

645
00:34:12,207 --> 00:34:14,323
And you don't get away with it all either.

646
00:34:14,399 --> 00:34:14,999
I know.

647
00:34:15,044 --> 00:34:17,490
Whether it's playing "I spy" after school

648
00:34:17,566 --> 00:34:20,593
or staying out all night at your boyfriend's hotel room,

649
