650
00:34:49,621 --> 00:34:50,154
Hello?

651
00:34:50,154 --> 00:34:52,019
Julie, I just thought of something.

652
00:34:52,095 --> 00:34:55,774
You know, you think you're dating prince charming.

653
00:34:56,665 --> 00:34:59,586
