I just called him.

655
00:35:04,465 --> 00:35:05,288
I ended it.

656
00:35:07,673 --> 00:35:08,994
It's over.

657
00:35:11,646 --> 00:35:13,549
As soon as he checks his messages.

658
00:35:14,132 --> 00:35:15,909
You broke up with him on his --

