He was probably looking to find your father so he could ask for his approval.

664
00:35:32,513 --> 00:35:34,717
I'll bet he didn't even know about the money.

665
00:35:34,793 --> 00:35:36,199
He lied about the house.

666
00:35:37,207 --> 00:35:38,567
He told you it was his?

667
00:35:38,643 --> 00:35:41,925
It was implied. He probably lied about the trust fund, too.

668
00:35:42,341 --> 00:35:44,720
