669
00:35:44,796 --> 00:35:47,453
It's one thing to lie and say you're not rich.

670
00:35:47,874 --> 00:35:50,170
The other way around is way less cool.

671
00:35:50,845 --> 00:35:52,152
I think I get it now.

672
00:35:52,989 --> 00:35:54,152
Money matters.

673
00:35:55,375 --> 00:35:56,582
Of course it matters.

674
00:36:01,168 --> 00:36:02,915
Alicia? Alicia?

675
00:36:06,620 --> 00:36:07,856
Anybody home?

676
00:36:32,656 --> 00:36:36,597
When your mom's an alcoholic, you spend a lot of time looking at bottles.

677
00:36:52,036 --> 00:36:54,106
"Julie, I wanted you to have these.

