00:36:54,346 --> 00:36:57,013
"Everything patrick collin nevin told you was true.

679
00:36:57,236 --> 00:36:58,596
"He does have a trust fund --

680
00:36:58,672 --> 00:37:00,861
"perhaps bigger than either of us imagined.

681
00:37:00,937 --> 00:37:02,243
"The enclosed article mentions

682
00:37:02,319 --> 00:37:04,122
"that he hates to flaunt his wealth "

