00:37:04,198 --> 00:37:05,736
or his celebrity friendships.

684
00:37:05,812 --> 00:37:09,336
"You both wanted to be sure "you were loved for who you really were.

685
00:37:09,412 --> 00:37:11,365
And it seems that one of you was."

