00:37:22,791 --> 00:37:23,868
Keith Mars.

687
00:37:25,018 --> 00:37:26,705
Mr. Pascal, yes.

688
00:37:27,442 --> 00:37:28,903
Uh, I know.

689
00:37:29,129 --> 00:37:30,822
It's been a little busy here.

690
00:37:33,645 --> 00:37:34,929
Um...

691
00:37:36,593 --> 00:37:37,589
here we go.

692
00:37:41,133 --> 00:37:41,976
I'm sorry, sir.

693
00:37:42,052 --> 00:37:44,903
