694
00:37:47,267 --> 00:37:48,179
Your uncle?

695
00:37:49,329 --> 00:37:51,050
Missing persons case?

696
00:37:51,126 --> 00:37:52,972
I'm very sorry, sir.

697
00:37:53,379 --> 00:37:55,030
It's a little filing mix-up.

698
00:37:55,624 --> 00:37:58,290
You were stuck inside Mr. Pastorelli's file.

699
00:38:03,009 --> 00:38:06,586
Your uncle al is alive and well in a retirement home in waikiki and,

700
00:38:06,662 --> 00:38:08,733
as far as I know, completely faithful.

701
00:38:11,147 --> 00:38:12,790
I have his number right here.

702
00:38:25,783 --> 00:38:26,383
Okay.

703
00:38:27,354 --> 00:38:30,213
Maybe I can use your help around the office...a bit.

704
00:38:31,671 --> 00:38:33,215
I'm sorry. Come again?

705
00:38:36,047 --> 00:38:38,443
You're never gonna tell me what happened to prompt this.

706
00:38:38,519 --> 00:38:39,353
Nope.

707
00:38:41,617 --> 00:38:45,636
Now, I'm just talking about a little help with research, filing, the phones.

708
00:38:45,872 --> 00:38:47,129
I do give good phone.

709
00:38:47,561 --> 00:38:49,047
Just a couple days a week.

710
00:38:49,123 --> 00:38:50,815
