00:39:09,636 --> 00:39:11,693
That call could've come from anywhere --

718
00:39:11,769 --> 00:39:14,466
a business line, a pay phone, or --

719
00:39:15,354 --> 00:39:16,292
oh, my god.

720
00:39:24,781 --> 00:39:25,662
Okay.

