00:39:35,006 --> 00:39:38,767
Saturday, september 24th, there was a 2-minute and 23-second phone call

725
00:39:38,843 --> 00:39:41,094
on Weevil's cellphone, made from your house.

726
00:39:41,170 --> 00:39:44,679
