727
00:39:44,755 --> 00:39:47,710
the same Curly Moran who's friends with your dad.

728
00:39:48,504 --> 00:39:49,629
Any explanation?

729
00:39:49,705 --> 00:39:51,496
Oh, my day is complete.

730
00:39:51,659 --> 00:39:53,688
Veronica Mars has accused me of evil.

731
00:39:54,938 --> 00:39:55,945
Where to start?

732
00:39:57,006 --> 00:39:59,528
Oh, yes -- who the hell is Curly Moran?

733
00:39:59,968 --> 00:40:01,234
And how do you know he knows my dad?

734
00:40:01,310 --> 00:40:04,988
And what conspiracy theory have you pulled out of your ass this time?

735
00:40:05,064 --> 00:40:08,053
The fact, evidenced by the poster in your house,

736
00:40:08,399 --> 00:40:12,005
is that Curly Moran was the stunt coordinator on "the long haul,"

737
00:40:12,081 --> 00:40:14,672
starring Aaron Echolls, circa 1982.

738
00:40:15,032 --> 00:40:16,468
Now, september 24th?

739
00:40:16,842 --> 00:40:18,433
Like I have any idea w--

740
00:40:20,959 --> 00:40:23,162
wait. I think I do remember that night.

741
00:40:23,238 --> 00:40:26,695
That was the night of my "life's short" party.

742
00:40:28,488 --> 00:40:29,259
Of course.

743
00:40:29,510 --> 00:40:32,807
