747
00:40:37,052 --> 00:40:39,575
And in the end, it wasn't just your social betters.

748
00:40:39,651 --> 00:40:42,636
In fact, your pal Weevil and his biker boys crashed it.

749
00:40:43,620 --> 00:40:44,771
Oh, and, uh...

750
00:40:47,158 --> 00:40:50,235
Lamb and a half-dozen deputies came by to break it up...

751
00:40:50,518 --> 00:40:51,835
or, at least, collect the kegs.

752
00:40:51,911 --> 00:40:54,659
There are five numbers registered to your house.

753
00:40:54,820 --> 00:40:57,282
