754
00:40:57,358 --> 00:40:59,427
Gee whillikers. It sounds like you're onto something.

755
00:40:59,503 --> 00:41:01,020
Maybe the pool boy did it.

756
00:41:01,945 --> 00:41:02,669
Well.

757
00:41:11,244 --> 00:41:12,627
You don't have anything?

758
00:41:13,183 --> 00:41:14,558
Not under "woods" either?

759
00:41:15,281 --> 00:41:18,247
By 1987, she was going by Alicia Fennel.

760
00:41:20,325 --> 00:41:21,352
Yeah, she does.

761
00:41:24,666 --> 00:41:25,396
What?

762
00:41:27,285 --> 00:41:28,124
Are you sure?

763
00:41:37,333 --> 00:41:38,240
Wallace?

764
00:41:42,792 --> 00:41:43,673
Yeah.

765
00:41:44,113 --> 00:41:44,892
Who are you?

766
00:41:49,938 --> 00:41:51,198
Take a look.

767
00:41:55,793 --> 00:41:57,310
Am I supposed to know you?

768
00:41:57,967 --> 00:41:59,216
You sure are, Wallace.

769
00:42:02,043 --> 00:42:03,040
